{"tid":2188550,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"大家會唔會覺得《大長今》係最優秀嘅韓劇之一？","createTime":"2020-09-04T10:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T11:41:02.000Z","uid":351978,"like":85,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"e51ee4cc0f81db3ce7f7bb4363dd003ecb0f131b","tid":2188550,"uid":351978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:06:09.000Z","msg":"《大長今》作為經典嘅韓劇，佢嘅內容係多元化，唔單止有愛情線，亦都有女權主義嘅元素。佢所強調嘅女權元素係唔會令人反感，更強調嘅係女性自強不息嘅奮鬥心態，而唔係單純講復仇之後就一定要原諒施害者等道理。而且呢套劇嘅起承轉合係完整同精彩嘅，因而令我覺得之後嘅韓劇真係比唔上《大長今》。唔知大家仲記唔記得同掛住呢一套韓劇？"},{"pid":"454e9e08cbc17aee179f598f0ad45638d5413a27","tid":2188550,"uid":325346,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T11:58:43.000Z","msg":"我飛佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n韓尚宮教長今做料理的心<br />\n閔大人對長今的癡情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n守護住長今<br />\n長今唔放棄的精神<br />\n而家無劇可以超越<br />\n而家重播都吊打所有劇"},{"pid":"51b3603d23a754611be6d1630402d8bfed0fd033","tid":2188550,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T11:59:22.000Z","msg":"AGREE"},{"pid":"8434817e6fb4ed125475f6a87faf611a6daae767","tid":2188550,"uid":31637,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:25:03.000Z","msg":"以前睇就覺得正姐<br />\n而家睇一撚定覺得好撚拖"},{"pid":"10ba5432aa1a84e2d1605025ca50f5919afe3afe","tid":2188550,"uid":76314,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"會，尤其係入面嘅師徒之情描繪得好好<br />\n仲有長今嘅求真同好學精神好深刻"},{"pid":"33c3f7950caa4bd9b70fa2a36e14d970323df5dc","tid":2188550,"uid":24457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:31:32.000Z","msg":"正係記得有集穿崩見到個宮女著高睜鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58d716ee2a3be16e4553e7f825049cdc199acfe","tid":2188550,"uid":325346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:14:03.000Z","msg":"而家今英、連生都好似結晒婚<br />\n李英愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class